---
title: Game Day Black Bean Chili with Southwestern Spices
description: If you’re looking for a recipe that’ll satisfy your whole team, chili is a safe bet. And when you drop the “con carne” and make it with hearty black beans, it becomes a dish that everyone can enjoy. Here, we’re adding in a dynamic spice duo of chili powder and cumin, then finishing it with slices of creamy avocado. It’ll hit the spot anytime, on game day and beyond!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/southwestern-black-bean-chili-0a4112cb.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/southwestern-black-bean-chili-0475c9ba.pdf
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 501 kcal
  fat: 20 g
  saturated fat: 3.5 g
  carbohydrates: 54 g
  sugar: 11 g
  protein: 21 g
  fiber: 29 g
  sodium: 239 mg
servings: 2
